               <head>Qissah-yi Abu Muslim</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Qiṣṣah-'i Abū Muslim by Muḥammad ibn Niẓām al-Dīn ibn Muḥammad</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2002009961 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85094675 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh87000556" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4641-item1">
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f7367"> Muḥammad ibn Niẓām al-Dīn ibn Muḥammad</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="person_f7367">‏محمّد ابن نظام الدّين ابن محمّد</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_9842">Qiṣṣah-'i Abū Muslim</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_9842">قصّهٔ ابو مسلم</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Rare romance of the <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658615.0x000001 viaf_67277812" role="subject">Abū Muslim ibn Asad ibn Junayd al-Marvazī</persName> (d. 137/755), who rebelled against Umayyad rule in <placeName>Khurasan</placeName>, based on a tradition attributed to <persName key="viaf_79194441" role="ant">Abū Ṭāhir Ṭarsūsī</persName>, by <persName key="person_f7367" role="aut">Muḥammad ibn Niẓām al-Dīn ibn Muḥammad "Ibn Niẓām"</persName>
                        </p>
                        <p>Arberry suggests this is the author's autograph </p>
                        <p>Dated colophon: 17 Z̲ū al-Ḥijjah 889/5 January 1485 by <persName key="person_f7367" role="aut">Muḥammad ibn Niẓām al-Dīn ibn Muḥammad "Ibn Niẓām" </persName>
                        </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
